{"tid":1814043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家唔好比捉鬼問題分化","createTime":"2020-01-06T17:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T17:18:14.000Z","uid":317774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63caa9b5ada25dc1e561d5cee08478fceec269e2","tid":1814043,"uid":317774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次出post，想講下捉鬼既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道依家好多臥底狗，老老實實真係捉唔完。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知捉鬼既人係咩心理、諗梗d咩，定係原來捉鬼既人先係鬼。 有d人話捉鬼一律當係鬼。 但無論你行為似鬼定捉鬼我都唔會理。 <br />\n你企得係我隔離我就當你係手足。 但係我希望各位多d留意身邊既人，如果你真係覺得某個人似鬼，你就遠離佢，唔洗專登捉鬼。 <br />\n(相信大家都明捉鬼高成本低回報)<br />\n<br />\n結論，鬼唔洗捉、捉鬼都唔洗捉，警惕周圍既人就得<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足唔好比狗分化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"a0a87e45aa6bb965234308e30204be591b7e4643","tid":1814043,"uid":317774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"p牌仔can't push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b76edca3e6ebfc50b66a2db6ce85cf1c1752682","tid":1814043,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14a2b0f78b8c49e76da02c5925f6aa373d6eb0ca","tid":1814043,"uid":317774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b76edca3e6ebfc50b66a2db6ce85cf1c1752682","tid":1814043,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a87e45aa6bb965234308e30204be591b7e4643","tid":1814043,"uid":317774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"p牌仔can't push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"洗唔